<pb facs="1038547" n="169r"/>
<div type="letter">
<p><lb/>Per <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089913338">fratrem</rs> meum mihi significavit nuper <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs>, se contentum esse, ut sibi
    <lb/>mittas <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">librum</rs> Tuum, quem libenter examinaturus et <subst><del>si</del><add>ubi</add></subst> opus fuerit correcturus sit,
    <lb/>de qua igitur re Te certiorem esse volui. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum spero <subst><del>d</del><add>T</add></subst>e accepisse nuperas meas
    <lb/><rs type="letter" key="B_1718-12-25_991170517038305501">litteras</rs>, in quibus ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sita Tua respondi.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et mihi favere perge.</salute> <dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728"><abbr>Pat.</abbr></rs> <date when="1719-01-03">3. <abbr>Jan.</abbr> 1719</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
</body>
</text></TEI>